.TH "cipso_v4_gentag_loc" 9 "cipso_v4_gentag_loc" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
cipso_v4_gentag_loc \- Generate a CIPSO local tag (non-standard)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" cipso_v4_gentag_loc
.BI "(const struct cipso_v4_doi *doi_def "  ","
.BI "const struct netlbl_lsm_secattr *secattr "  ","
.BI "unsigned char *buffer "  ","
.BI "u32 buffer_len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "doi_def" 12
the DOI definition
.IP "secattr" 12
the security attributes
.IP "buffer" 12
the option buffer
.IP "buffer_len" 12
length of buffer in bytes
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Generate a CIPSO option using the local tag.  Returns the size of the tag
on success, negative values on failure.
